\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 11}For well He knoweth vain men:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
He looks upon sin and He marks it.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 12}Even a senseless man may be taught,
