{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
And let wrong dwell no more in thy tent,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 15}Then thy face thou wouldst lift without blemish,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
