As floods that are passed wouldst thou think of it.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 17}Brighter than noon would thy life rise,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
