\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 20}But the eyes of the wicked shall fail,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
The place of their refuge is perished.
\par}

