The man of ease mocks at his fate:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
There are thrusts for the feet that are slipping.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}It is tents of robbers that prosper,
\par}

