\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 8}The creatures that crawl \uc1\u8211* they will teach thee;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
The fish of the sea \uc1\u8211* they will tell thee.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 9}For which of them all doth not know
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
