\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 11}Doth not the ear test words
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
As the palate tastes food for itself?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 12}Doth wisdom depend upon years,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
Understanding on length of days?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 13}With Him is wisdom and might,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
Understanding and counsel are His.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 14}See! He breaketh down, and who buildeth?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
Imprisons, and none can set free.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 15}See! He holds back the floods and they dry;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
