\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 21}He poureth contempt upon princes;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
He looseth the belt of the strong.
