{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 22}He revealeth the deep things of darkness,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
The gloom-wrapped He bringeth to light.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 23}He makes nations great and destroys them;
\par}

