\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}Now listen to this mine indictment,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
Attend to the plea of my lips.
\par}

