{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 12b}Till the heavens be no more, he awakes not,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 12c}Nor ever is roused from his sleep.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
