\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
Out of sight, till Thine anger be past,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
And then call me to mind in Thine own set time!
\par}

{\pard
