\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
And with speech that is all unavailing?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4}See! thou art destroying religion,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
Disturbing devout contemplation.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 5}Thy guilt instructeth thy mouth,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
And thou choosest the tongue of the crafty.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}Thine own mouth condems thee \uc1\u8211* not I,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
And thine own lips are witness against thee.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 7}Wast thou the first man to be born?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
Wast thou fashioned before the hills?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 8}Wast thou one of the heavenly council?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
Was wisdom revealed unto thee?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 9}What knowest thou that we know not?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
What insight is thine and not ours?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 10}With us are the grey and the aged,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
More mighty in years than thy father.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 11}Dost thou spurn the divine consolations,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
The word that dealt with thee so gently?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 12}How fierce the emotions that sweep thee!
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
