\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 14}What is man that he should be clean,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
Or just \uc1\u8211* one of woman born?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 15}See! He putteth no trust in His saints,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
And the heavens are not clean in His sight:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 16}How much less one abhorrent and tainted\uc1\u8211*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
A man that drinks evil like water!
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 17}Now listen to what I will show thee,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
The thing I have seen I will tell\uc1\u8211*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 18}Even tales that were told by the wise
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
And not hidden from them by their fathers,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 19}Who had the land all to themselves,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
When no stranger had yet come among them.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 20}All his days is the wicked in pain,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
All the years for the tyrant appointed.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 21}In his ears is the sound of terrors,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
In peace comes the spoiler upon him.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 22}He cannot escape from the darkness
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
And he is reserved for the sword.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 23}Appointed as food for the vulture\uc1\u8211*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
He knows that his doom is at hand.
