{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 24a}Constraint and distress overpower him;
\par}

{\pard
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 25}For he stretched out his hand against God,
