{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
He pours out my gall on the ground.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 14}One breach after another He makes on me,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
Rushing at me like a warrior.
\par}

