\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 16}My face is red with weeping,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
And over mine eye-lids is darkness\uc1\u8211*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 17}Though wrong there is none in my hands,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
And though my prayer be pure.
