\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}Why are we counted as breasts,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
And deemed by thee to be dullards?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
