\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}The light in his tent shall be dark,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
And the lamp o\uc1\u8217*er his head shall go out.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 7}His great swinging strides become shortened;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
